platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: A game about life, loss & hope
La vie, le regret et l'espoir.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: An Apple Design Award winner, this moving puzzler proves sometimes the best stories dont need words. Developer Broken Rules has created a hand-drawn world that bubbles with whimsy and heart. Altering the landscape to reveal hidden paths makes for fascinating, peaceful gameplay. We love exploring the storybook settings and uncovering each touching memory. Its unforgettable, and wed move mountains just to relive the experience.

Les meilleures histoires peuvent se raconter sans paroles. Cest ce que nous prouve le studio Broken Rules avec ce casse-tte touchant, laurat dun Apple Design Award. Dans un monde entirement dessin  la main, dbordant de fantaisie et dmotions, vous pouvez modifier votre paysage et rvler des chemins cachs. Une aventure inoubliable et relaxante quon ne demande qu recommencer.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Experience a lifetime of memory as you embark on a gorgeous journey.
Experience the meditative voyage of a gentleman puzzling through his past.
Accompagnez un homme dans le voyage au cur de ses souvenirs.
